welcome_message_body: Welcome to Manado Light, where the serene beauty of the city's coastline and the warm hospitality of its people await you. Known for its vibrant marine life and delicious culinary scene, we invite you to explore and immerse yourself in all that this charming city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!
